snippet.title: Blocked Up · Game · Gameplay
snippet.description:
Play this game for free here: https://palemoongames.itch.io/blocked-up
Blocked Up is a challenging mix of a Tetrix-like game and a match-3 puzzle game. Survive for as long as you can by matching same-colored blocks and avoiding falling ones. This game is made by Pale Moon Games: https://palemoongames.itch.io/
